      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ICE COOL BLUE (1) boasts a consistent overall record including six wins from 26 starts, the latest hitting the minor money when second (30.96) over 530m at this track. Looks a key player drawing the cherry. AGENT TWENTY ONE (3) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 1.5 lengths at Gawler in a handy 30.85 beating Big Boss Giblet. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Can measure up again. ADHANA PATRICK (2) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (30.98) at this track in a Grade 6. Lines up from box 2 for the first time. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. SOKAI (8) deserves plenty of thought at his first run at this distance.",
